                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>ecimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Fa<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>Consors <expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rorum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Augustal</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>mag</abbr><ex>ister</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>ator</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omanorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>conven</abbr><ex>tus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Hel</abbr><ex>vetici</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>EX<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="0"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>VIS<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 2: SA miteinander verschränkt; Text 3: I-longa. (B): Walser; CIL 13, 11478: Z. 5: Hel(vetici) ex vis[u]; die Positionierung der Fragmente Tex2 und 3 innerhalb des Inschriftträgers ist jedoch nicht sicher. Funddatum: 1889/90.</p>
